          "At each assessment",
          "Authoors mantained a continuous count of the number of accesses up to the point of measurement - 99% of accesses were done to News and Teaching. \n\nThe analysis was done at multiple levels:\n\n- At each assessment using only the sequence of assessment scores. \n\n- At each assessment using all data points\n\n- At each assessment by combining the 2 types of VLE accesses into a single one.\n",
