          "No Assessment Strategy",
          "{Average  Accuracy: 0.84 - Random Forest}",
          "Authors create a model using just a very small dataset and a very minute numberr of predictors:\n\nAttendance records, Historical Assessment Scores in the course and VLE logs are used.\n\nAuthors test different combinations of features on 3 algorithms to assess the performance of their models.\n\nNo assessment strategy is used . no train-test separation. ",
          "- No Assessment Method\n\n- Small dataset \n\n- Single course context\n\n- Small number of algorithms used\n\n\n\n\n"
